JO6SYVK-8xX-kQ">Quá Lê miếu nhân đề - 過黎廟因題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-%C3%94n/author-gnFL88QsL3FYvt7WpS9SHg">Bạch Đông Ôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/T%C3%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-MY0fsHhB1aZbLrdFloVv5A">Tái thượng - 塞上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/author--S-Kylm25PBOdm26_KrpXQ">Tư Không Đồ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Th%E1%BB%A5c-t%C4%83ng-L%C6%B0-Kh%C3%A2u-s%C6%B0-huynh/poem-C2CeOBfxv-lY1Z3z_x3taA">Tặng Thục tăng Lư Khâu sư huynh - 贈蜀僧閭丘師兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Ph%C3%B9ng/V%C3%A2n-Nam-t%E1%BB%B1-l%E1%BA%A1c-th%C3%A0nh/poem-_HPsLMpsPiF1X00kpybJig">Vân Nam tự lạc thành - 雲南寺落成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-bM1XTMtT_e9aq9mDCC9YaA">Trần Hữu Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-B%E1%BA%A1ch-M%C3%A3-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-eMZ5ilGuF1oJidKHFyYiwQ">Vịnh Bạch Mã từ - 詠白馬祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/author-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Phan Thúc Trực</a>)<br></div>	</div>
